divs: sighting detailsdriving south bound on us1 north miami beach florida just north of the intersection of biscayne and 163rd street. notice objects to my right. took 2 pictures with iphone. in first picture 4 objects. in second picture 3 objects. total 7 objects. fog moving in from left (east). other vehicles in the picture. other lights. railroad crossings. objects moved quickly southbound and vanished. i usually am observant. trained to look at my surroundings. single engine pilot since 8\1970.
